{"__ud_title":"Skills、MCP、Projects、Prompts","__ud_tags":["Tools","aiskills","Cloude code"],"__ud_update_time":1773631738536,"__ud_create_time":1773631736512,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"SkillsMCPProjectsPrompts"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills、MCP、Projects、Prompts"}]},{"type":"blockquote","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"古法编程纯手工"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"古法编程纯手工:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这四个概念相互关联：Prompt指导AI，Skill提供能力，MCP整合工具，Projects保存经验。Projects是AI的记忆系统，保存项目历史、配置和数据，便于复用和团队协作，与Skill的区别在于更注重长期积累而非即时功能。"}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"PromptAI-的说明书"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt：AI 的「说明书」"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"21-什么是-Prompt"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2.1 什么是 Prompt？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt 就是你给 AI 的指令，告诉它你想要什么。"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 简单 Prompt\n帮我写一个 React 组件\n\n# 复杂 Prompt\n你是一个资深的 React 开发者，精通 TypeScript 和性能优化。\n请帮我写一个用户列表组件，要求：\n1. 使用 TypeScript\n2. 支持分页\n3. 支持搜索\n4. 使用 React Query\n5. 注重性能优化\n...\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"22-Prompt-的问题"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2.2 Prompt 的问题"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"问题 1：每次都要重复"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 今天\n你是一个资深的 React 开发者...（100 行）\n\n# 明天\n你是一个资深的 React 开发者...（100 行，又来一遍）\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"问题 2：容易遗漏"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 第一次\n记得加 TypeScript 类型、错误处理、loading 状态\n\n# 第二次\n忘了写，AI 生成的代码没有错误处理\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"问题 3：难以维护"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 一个月后\n这个 Prompt 为什么要这样写？\n能删掉这条规则吗？\n不知道，不敢动\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"23-Prompt-的适用场景"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2.3 Prompt 的适用场景"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"适合"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"一次性任务"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"简单需求"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"快速验证"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"❌ "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"不适合"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"重复任务"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"复杂规则"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"团队协作"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"三Skill可复用的专家"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"三、Skill：可复用的「专家」"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"31-什么是-Skill"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3.1 什么是 Skill？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skill 是把 Prompt 封装成可复用的模块，就像给 AI 安装一个「专家插件」。"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!-- .cursor/skills/react-expert/SKILL.md -->\n# React Expert Skill\n\n你是一个资深的 React 开发者，精通：\n- TypeScript\n- React Hooks\n- 性能优化\n- 测试\n\n## 代码规范\n1. 使用函数式组件\n2. 优先使用 TypeScript\n3. 遵循 Airbnb 代码规范\n...\n\n## 性能优化\n1. 事件处理函数用 useCallback\n2. 复杂计算用 useMemo\n3. 纯展示组件用 React.memo\n...\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"32-Skill-的优势"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3.2 Skill 的优势"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"优势 1：一次编写，到处使用"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 使用 Skill\n/react-expert 写一个用户列表组件\n/react-expert 写一个订单列表组件\n/react-expert 写一个商品列表组件\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"优势 2：效果稳定"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 每次都应用相同的规则\n✅ TypeScript\n✅ 性能优化\n✅ 错误处理\n✅ 代码规范\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"优势 3：易于维护"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!-- 更新 Skill -->\n## 性能优化\n1. 事件处理函数用 useCallback\n2. 复杂计算用 useMemo\n3. 纯展示组件用 React.memo\n4. 长列表用虚拟滚动  ← 新增规则\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"所有使用这个 Skill 的地方都会自动应用新规则。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"优势 4：团队共享"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"bash"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 团队共享 Skill 库\ngit clone https://github.com/company/cursor-skills.git\ncp -r cursor-skills/.cursor/skills ~/.cursor/skills\n\n# 所有人都能用\n/react-expert\n/vue-expert\n/node-expert\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"33-Skill-vs-Prompt"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3.3 Skill vs Prompt"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"维度PromptSkill复用性复制粘贴直接调用维护性难以维护集中维护一致性容易遗漏始终一致团队协作难以共享易于共享学习曲线低中"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"四MCPAI-的工具箱"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"四、MCP：AI 的「工具箱」"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"41-什么是-MCP"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4.1 什么是 MCP？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MCP（Model Context Protocol）是 Anthropic 推出的协议，让 AI 能够调用外部工具。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"类比"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt/Skill：告诉 AI「怎么做」"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MCP：给 AI「工具」，让它自己做"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"42-MCP-的工作原理"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4.2 MCP 的工作原理"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"arduino"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户：帮我查一下今天的天气\n\nAI：好的，我需要调用天气 API\n    ↓\nMCP Server：调用 weather API\n    ↓\n返回：北京，晴，25°C\n    ↓\nAI：今天北京天气晴朗，温度 25°C\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"43-MCP-的应用场景"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4.3 MCP 的应用场景"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"场景 1：文件操作"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户：帮我创建一个 React 项目\n\nAI：\n1. 调用 MCP 的 filesystem 工具\n2. 创建目录结构\n3. 生成配置文件\n4. 安装依赖\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"场景 2：数据库查询"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户：查询最近 7 天的订单数据\n\nAI：\n1. 调用 MCP 的 database 工具\n2. 执行 SQL 查询\n3. 返回结果\n4. 生成报表\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"场景 3：API 调用"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户：帮我发一条推特\n\nAI：\n1. 调用 MCP 的 twitter 工具\n2. 发送推文\n3. 返回推文链接\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"44-MCP-的配置"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4.4 MCP 的配置"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"json"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"// .cursor/mcp.json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"filesystem\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-filesystem\", \"/path/to/workspace\"]\n    },\n    \"database\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-postgres\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"DATABASE_URL\": \"postgresql://user:pass@localhost:5432/db\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"github\": {\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@modelcontextprotocol/server-github\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"GITHUB_TOKEN\": \"your-token\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"45-MCP-vs-API"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4.5 MCP vs API"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"维度传统 APIMCP调用方式手动编码AI 自动调用错误处理手动处理AI 自动重试参数构造手动构造AI 自动推断结果解析手动解析AI 自动理解"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"五ProjectsAI-的记忆"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"五、Projects：AI 的「记忆」"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"51-什么是-Projects"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5.1 什么是 Projects？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Projects 是 Cursor 的新功能，让 AI 记住项目的上下文。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"类比"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt：一次性对话"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skill：可复用的规则"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"MCP：可调用的工具"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Projects：持久化的记忆"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"52-Projects-的作用"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5.2 Projects 的作用"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"作用 1：记住项目结构"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 第一次对话\n用户：这个项目的目录结构是什么？\nAI：（扫描项目）\n    src/\n    ├── components/\n    ├── pages/\n    ├── utils/\n    └── types/\n\n# 第二次对话（几天后）\n用户：帮我在 components 目录下创建一个新组件\nAI：好的，我记得 components 目录在 src 下\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"作用 2：记住代码风格"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AI 分析项目后\n- 使用 TypeScript\n- 使用函数式组件\n- 使用 Tailwind CSS\n- 使用 React Query\n\n# 之后生成的代码都会遵循这些风格\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"作用 3：记住业务逻辑"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AI 分析项目后\n- 用户认证使用 JWT\n- API 基础 URL 是 /api/v1\n- 错误处理使用 toast 提示\n- 表单验证使用 Zod\n\n# 之后生成的代码都会遵循这些逻辑\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"53-Projects-的配置"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5.3 Projects 的配置"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!-- .cursor/projects/my-project.md -->\n# My Project\n\n## 项目信息\n- 名称：电商管理系统\n- 技术栈：React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS\n- 状态管理：Zustand\n- 数据请求：React Query\n\n## 目录结构\nsrc/\n├── components/  # 通用组件\n├── pages/       # 页面组件\n├── hooks/       # 自定义 Hooks\n├── utils/       # 工具函数\n├── types/       # TypeScript 类型\n└── api/         # API 接口\n\n## 代码规范\n1. 组件使用函数式组件\n2. 所有 props 都要定义类型\n3. 使用 Tailwind CSS，不写内联样式\n4. API 调用使用 React Query\n\n## 业务规则\n1. 用户认证使用 JWT\n2. Token 存储在 localStorage\n3. 未登录跳转到 /login\n4. 错误提示使用 toast\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"54-Projects-vs-Skill"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5.4 Projects vs Skill"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"维度SkillProjects作用域通用规则项目特定内容编码规范项目上下文复用性跨项目单项目维护手动更新AI 自动学习"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"六四者的关系"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"六、四者的关系"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prompt（基础）\n  ↓\nSkill（可复用的 Prompt）\n  ↓\nMCP（可调用的工具）\n  ↓\nProjects（持久化的上下文）\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"组合使用"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户：/react-expert 帮我在这个项目中创建一个用户管理模块\n\nAI 的工作流程：\n1. 读取 Projects：了解项目结构和规范\n2. 应用 Skill：使用 React Expert 的规则\n3. 调用 MCP：创建文件、安装依赖\n4. 生成代码：符合项目规范的代码\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"七实战案例"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"七、实战案例"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"71-案例-1从零搭建项目"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"7.1 案例 1：从零搭建项目"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 1. 创建 Project\n用户：创建一个电商管理系统项目\n\nAI：\n- 调用 MCP filesystem 创建目录\n- 生成 package.json\n- 安装依赖\n- 创建 Projects 配置\n\n# 2. 使用 Skill 生成代码\n用户：/react-expert 创建用户管理模块\n\nAI：\n- 读取 Projects 了解项目结构\n- 应用 Skill 的规则\n- 生成符合规范的代码\n\n# 3. 持续开发\n用户：添加订单管理模块\n\nAI：\n- 参考用户管理模块的风格\n- 保持一致性\n- 自动应用相同的规范\n"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3,"id":"72-案例-2团队协作"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"7.2 案例 2：团队协作"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 团队 Skill 库\n.cursor/skills/\n├── react-expert/\n├── vue-expert/\n├── node-expert/\n├── testing-expert/\n└── security-expert/\n\n# 项目 Projects 配置\n.cursor/projects/\n├── frontend.md\n├── backend.md\n└── mobile.md\n\n# MCP 工具\n.cursor/mcp.json\n- filesystem\n- database\n- github\n- slack\n"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"团队成员可以："}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"共享 Skill 库（统一规范）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"共享 Projects 配置（统一上下文）"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"共享 MCP 工具（统一工具链）"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"八总结"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"八、总结"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"AI 开发的四大概念："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Prompt"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"基础的指令"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"适合一次性任务"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"难以复用和维护"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Skill"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可复用的专家"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"适合重复任务"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"易于维护和共享"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"MCP"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可调用的工具"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让 AI 能操作外部系统"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"扩展 AI 的能力"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Projects"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"持久化的上下文"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"让 AI 记住项目信息"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"保持代码一致性"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"使用建议"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"基础任务：Prompt"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"重复任务：Skill"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"外部操作：MCP"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"项目开发：Projects"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"组合使用"},{"type":"text","text":"："}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":null},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"  "}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Projects（项目上下文）\n  + Skill（编码规范）\n  + MCP（工具调用）\n  = 高效的 AI 开发\n\n"}]}]}